{"tid":1319623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公道少少，救警個cctvb攝記有份救墮橋𡃁仔","createTime":"2019-07-15T07:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:16:37.000Z","uid":6003,"like":110,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"7a108f1508aa792150e516e3abba50fd555c0a74","tid":1319623,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"「...後來，更知道救了警察的攝記，就是前一天有份伸手把差點在上水墮橋的16歲少年拉上來的同一人．記者們都認同，少年跌落橋，如果你剛巧在旁，伸手救是合乎情理，那是一條人命．警察被圍打至重傷，情況就更複雜．而諷刺是，出手救人的攝記，乃是今場運動中被狠批「出賣港人」的傳媒機構．」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1435535666534854/posts/2381566121931799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1435535666534854%2Fposts%2F2381566121931799&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=fc37cda8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1435535666534854/posts/2381566121931799</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iixWpUQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiixWpUQ.png&h=a70d514d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個攝記示範到咩叫中立<br />\n有生命危險既示威者同警犬都照救<br />\n但HKVDC_2017你咁開post做鳩人會否太仆街<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB攝記疑放棄傳媒中立，違返專業介入衝突護黑警<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a26d513e12c56be8db0716b6171c1cea8044a3ee","tid":1319623,"uid":238051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"deed70f8c51bd808ea3d3cdbdfcbc94e8b4166a8","tid":1319623,"uid":212182,"like":153,"dislike":1,"score":152,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"記者點都有d人性既。不過cctvb無得洗底架喇"},{"pid":"af3ec0fd85cd6519c77ce0d84bc2ce7066a2fd1b","tid":1319623,"uid":27451,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"repl